paragraph.content:
to permit access to the mentally incapacitated person for the purpose of
                    any visit by or on behalf of the Director in the exercise of his powers and
                    duties under the Ordinance;

to notify the Director of any change of his or the mentally incapacitated
                    person’s place of residence not later than 14 days after such change takes
                    place;

to furnish the Director with such reports or information with regard to the
                    mentally incapacitated person as the Director may from time to time
                    require;

subparagraph.content:
there is any change in the nature and location of the mentally
                        incapacitated person’s employment or training or educational course;
                        or
